data.description: Discover comfort in this 3-bed, 2-bath home with a spacious living room and a flexible extra space perfect for dining or a second living area. Beyond the walls, discover a generous backyard, providing ample space for outdoor activities and enjoying serene moments. Nestled in a tranquil neighborhood, this residence offers a peaceful retreat while still being conveniently close to essential amenities. Embrace the warmth of this inviting abode, where every room tells a story of comfort and convenience.
